sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client
    participant GW as vllm-orchestrator-gateway<br/>8090/TCP HTTP
    participant Orch as FMS Guardrails Orchestrator<br/>8085/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Detector as Guardrails Detectors<br/>(e.g., regex-language)
    participant LLM as vLLM Inference Server

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over Client,LLM: Flow 1: Non-Streaming Chat Completion with Detection
        Client->>GW: POST /{route}/v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP plaintext<br/>Authorization header (optional)
        Note over GW: Inject detector config<br/>from route YAML into payload
        GW->>Orch: POST /api/v2/chat/completions-detection<br/>HTTP or HTTPS (Optional mTLS)<br/>mTLS client cert + forwarded Auth header
        Orch->>Detector: Run content detection<br/>(input detectors)
        Detector-->>Orch: Detection results
        Orch->>LLM: Inference request
        LLM-->>Orch: Generated response
        Orch->>Detector: Run content detection<br/>(output detectors)
        Detector-->>Orch: Detection results
        Orch-->>GW: JSON response with detections
        Note over GW: If detections found,<br/>replace content with<br/>fallback message
        GW-->>Client: JSON response<br/>HTTP plaintext
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over Client,LLM: Flow 2: Streaming Chat Completion (SSE)
        Client->>GW: POST /{route}/v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP plaintext, stream=true<br/>Authorization header (optional)
        Note over GW: Inject detector config<br/>from route YAML into payload
        GW->>Orch: POST /api/v2/chat/completions-detection<br/>HTTP or HTTPS (Optional mTLS)<br/>stream=true
        Orch->>Detector: Run content detection
        Orch->>LLM: Streaming inference request
        loop SSE chunks
            LLM-->>Orch: SSE chunk
            Orch-->>GW: SSE chunk (with detections)
            Note over GW: If detections in chunk,<br/>replace with fallback
            GW-->>Client: SSE chunk<br/>text/event-stream
        end
        GW-->>Client: [DONE]
    end
